comment_data.body: Android Studio canary builds are not currently supported in our stable channel. You can avoid this error by uninstalling the Flutter plugin or switching to the [dev channel](https://github.com/flutter/flutter-intellij/wiki/Dev-Channel).

title: Plugin error each time a Android (not flutter) project is opened in Android Studio
